name: Fart West
description:
You are a young girl who has been abducted by the invading aliens and has received the power of expelling overpowered flatulences. You also have a chainsaw.

Controls:

Space - Jump and fly

Control - Attack

Arrows - Move

This game was made for the VII Student Game Jam, hosted at Valencia by AEV (@asociacionAEV), by:

Adrián Sáchez - @adriansansal

Marta Castilla - @alabamakiller

Miguel Montoya - @calighula

Alex Colombini - @atcolombini
